        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/11/12",
        "text": [
          "١١. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): إِذَا قَدَرْتَ عَلَى عَدُوِّكَ فَاجْعَلِ الْعَفْوَ عَنْهُ شُكْراً لِلْقُدْرَةِ عَلَيْهِ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "11. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: When you gain power over your adversary pardon him by way of thanks for being able to overpower him. [1]"
          ]
        }
